{
  "stem": "19807.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 230.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were extremely drastic.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If-- if you can imagine I'm playing with the children, the Bulgarian children.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, they begin to belong to an organization.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was called [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They had to wear like a uniform, like a military uniform.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they took extreme pride in that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And those friends that I was with them, they would-- they would shy away from me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Well, there are several of them actually that they didn't.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They would go home and they change the uniform.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We still go and play.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But you could see that it was totally different.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There was not that camaraderie, that closeness as before.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And that was the extreme, the ones that they were really tolerant.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But most of them became overnight, if you might say, so enamored with that Fascist idea of wearing uniforms and taking care of-- of the nation by getting rid of all this Jews and by-- by-- by restricting the Jews even though there were quite a few that they were really very reluctant to admit to all that, but they very openly things changed so much for us that, like I said, the first thing with my father, then my uncle that he was no longer a chairman of the board of Bulgarian bank.",
      "word_count": 94
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They-- they dismissed him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He had to resign.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And then my-- my other uncle lost all his properties.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They confiscated everything.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They lived in a beautiful home and they had to move to a much, much smaller area.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Lucky they still live there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Then they were interned, because some of the most prominent Jews in the community were interned for a certain amount of time, being that they thought they were going to be shipped out to the camp, but they were not.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
